# Code Owners
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more owners.
# Owners are automatically requested for review when code matching
# the pattern is modified.
#
# Pattern format: https://docs.github.com/en/github/creating-cloning-and-archiving-repositories/about-code-owners
#
# Order is important; the last matching pattern takes precedence.

# Global owners - fallback for unmatched files
* @neurondb/maintainers

